{"info": {"author": "Alma", "author_email": "contact@getalma.eu", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8"], "description": "# alma-python-client\n\n[![Travis Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/alma/alma-python-client.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/alma/alma-python-client) [![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/alma-client.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/alma-client)\n\nPython API Client for the Alma API\n\n## Install\n\n```bash\npip install alma-client\n```\n\n## Demo\n\n\n```python\nfrom alma import Client\n\nalma_client = Client(api_key=\"sk_test..\")\npayments = alma_client.payments.fetch_all()\n\nfor p in payments:\n    print(f\"{p.id}: Paiement en {len(p.payment_plan)} fois\")\n\n\npayment_data = {\n    \"purchase_amount\": 10000,\n    \"return_url\": \"http://merchant.com/payment-success\",\n    \"shipping_address\": {\n        \"first_name\": \"Martin\",\n        \"last_name\": \"Dupond\",\n        \"line1\": \"1 rue de Rivoli\",\n        \"postal_code\": \"75004\",\n        \"city\": \"Paris\"\n    }\n}\n\neligibility = alma_client.payments.eligibility(payment_data)\nif eligibility.eligible:\n    alma_client.payments.create(payment_data)\n```\n\n\n# Changelog\n\n1.1.0 (2020-03-25)\n------------------\n\n- Add support for Python 3.5+\n\n\n1.0.1 (2020-03-24)\n------------------\n\n- Automatically detects the API mode from the api_key.\n\n\n1.0.0 (2020-03-24)\n------------------\n\n- Create a Python client for Alma\n- Handle Order entity for Payment\n- Handle the refund endpoint\n- Handle pagination for orders\n- Handle the send-sms API for payments.\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/alma/alma-python-client", "keywords": "", "license": "MIT", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "alma-client", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/alma-client/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/alma-client/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/alma/alma-python-client"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/alma-client/1.1.0/", "requires_dist": ["requests"], "requires_python": "", "summary": "Python API client for the Alma Installments API", "version": "1.1.0", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>alma-python-client</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/alma/alma-python-client\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Travis Build Status\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/efcfe26cf927b8ad4bada739c0f2df7188e358e8/68747470733a2f2f7472617669732d63692e6f72672f616c6d612f616c6d612d707974686f6e2d636c69656e742e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\"></a> <a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/alma-client\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"PyPI\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/9a99862e9799b6337398c4a40402dbe977d7200e/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f707970692f762f616c6d612d636c69656e742e737667\"></a></p>\n<p>Python API Client for the Alma API</p>\n<h2>Install</h2>\n<pre>pip install alma-client\n</pre>\n<h2>Demo</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">alma</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Client</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">alma_client</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Client</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">api_key</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"sk_test..\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">payments</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">alma_client</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">payments</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">fetch_all</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">for</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"ow\">in</span> <span class=\"n\">payments</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"sa\">f</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">{</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"si\">}</span><span class=\"s2\">: Paiement en </span><span class=\"si\">{</span><span class=\"nb\">len</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">payment_plan</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"si\">}</span><span class=\"s2\"> fois\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"n\">payment_data</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"purchase_amount\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"mi\">10000</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"return_url\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"http://merchant.com/payment-success\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">\"shipping_address\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"s2\">\"first_name\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Martin\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"s2\">\"last_name\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Dupond\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"s2\">\"line1\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"1 rue de Rivoli\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"s2\">\"postal_code\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"75004\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"s2\">\"city\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Paris\"</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">eligibility</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">alma_client</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">payments</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">eligibility</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">payment_data</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"n\">eligibility</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">eligible</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">alma_client</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">payments</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">create</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">payment_data</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<h1>Changelog</h1>\n<h2>1.1.0 (2020-03-25)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Add support for Python 3.5+</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>1.0.1 (2020-03-24)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Automatically detects the API mode from the api_key.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>1.0.0 (2020-03-24)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a Python client for Alma</li>\n<li>Handle Order entity for Payment</li>\n<li>Handle the refund endpoint</li>\n<li>Handle pagination for orders</li>\n<li>Handle the send-sms API for payments.</li>\n</ul>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6882897, "releases": {"1.0.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "871224438504bae49d1322dd14021e65", "sha256": "515cfa98bc852b891690e7fb4011a1f67d861cba6ac5fadf031eae9c08351f70"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "alma_client-1.0.0-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "871224438504bae49d1322dd14021e65", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 13486, "upload_time": "2020-03-24T13:44:24", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-03-24T13:44:24.549239Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/80/c8/24824f1ebbc17ad82a4d8f6c5089506733362e39b07e31f96dde0b432d3c/alma_client-1.0.0-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "bf8084c4d1a8ee6d5457d867f2d49443", "sha256": "5f60701c6d1892fd53e0dca425395ed